gue that guides later writing and revision. But when teachers accompany writers, teaching CW becomes even more a negotiation of the personal because this teacher who is listener and mentor is also a model for some students of the writer and even the person they would like to become - and still the Authority who gives the grades.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Apr 2022) 0aCreative writingxStudy and teaching. 0aWriting centers. 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Writing / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertMultiLingual Matters Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2015z978311066313608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertMultiLingual Matters eBook Package Backlist 2000-2014z978311060671340uhttps://doi.org/10.21832/978184769439340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781847694393423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781847694393/original  a978-3-11-060671-3  MultiLingual Matters eBook Package Backlist 2000-2014c2000d2014  a978-3-11-066313-6  MultiLingual Matters Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2015c2000d2015  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LS  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_LS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK